---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Colorado Muslim Society | Home"
  description="A welcoming masjid and community organization serving Denver families, students, and visitors."
  heroBlendNav
>
  <section class="hero" style={`--hero-image: url('${baseUrl}images/cms-home-banner.jpg')`}>
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Serving Denver Since 1964</p>
      <h1>Colorado Muslim Society</h1>
      <p class="hero-intro">A welcoming masjid and community organization in Denver, Colorado.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container home-content-stack">
      <article class="welcome-panel welcome-panel--full">
        <h2>Welcome to Colorado Muslim Society</h2>
        <p>
          Colorado Muslim Society was established in 1964, serving the Muslim community in Denver and its
          surrounding regions. CMS provides many services for the local community, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Salat services 5 times a day</li>
          <li>Sunday school for children</li>
          <li>Janazah and burial services</li>
          <li>Islamic advice</li>
          <li>Knowledge about Islam</li>
          <li>Sehri and iftar food during Ramadan</li>
          <li>Eid prayers</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="welcome-close">We look forward to seeing you there soon.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="welcome-panel welcome-panel--full home-masjid-message">
        <p>
          As you are aware, Colorado Muslim Society (Masjid Abu-Bakr) has been taking on much needed projects
          to get the masjid up to codes and standards. The masjid has recently completed two major projects;
          dome repair and parking lot reconstruction.
        </p>
        <p>
          The Masjid still needs your help to replenish the funds used to complete these projects and take on
          more repairs in and around Masjid property. May Allah the Almighty reward your continued support.
        </p>
        <p class="home-hadith">
          The Messenger of Allah, Muhammad (peace and blessings of Allah be upon him), said: &ldquo;Whoever
          builds a Masjid for the sake of Allah, Allah will build for him a house in Paradise.&rdquo;
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
